# UIForceTouchCapability.unknown

**Case**

The availability of 3D Touch is unknown.

## Declaration

```swift
case unknown
```

## Discussion

A view has this trait after you create it but before you add it your app’s view hierarchy.

## Availability options

- **UIForceTouchCapability.available**: 3D Touch is available on the device.
- **UIForceTouchCapability.unavailable**: 3D Touch isn’t available on the device.
